<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Netigo Updates History</title>
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Outfit:wght@300;400;500;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/style.css">
    <style>
        .timeline {
            position: relative;
            max-width: 800px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 40px 0;
        }

        .timeline::after {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            width: 4px;
            background-color: var(--border-color);
            top: 0;
            bottom: 0;
            left: 31px;
            border-radius: 4px;
        }

        .timeline-item {
            padding: 10px 40px 40px 80px;
            position: relative;
            background-color: inherit;
            width: 100%;
        }

        .timeline-item::after {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            width: 20px;
            height: 20px;
            right: auto;
            background-color: var(--bg-main);
            border: 4px solid var(--color-investment);
            top: 15px;
            left: 23px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            z-index: 1;
        }

        .timeline-content {
            padding: 30px;
            background: var(--bg-secondary);
            border: 1px solid var(--border-color);
            border-radius: 16px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
        }

        .version-badge {
            display: inline-block;
            background: var(--color-investment);
            color: #fff;
            padding: 4px 12px;
            border-radius: 20px;
            font-size: 14px;
            font-weight: 600;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }

        .update-date {
            color: var(--text-muted);
            font-size: 14px;
            margin-left: 10px;
        }

        .timeline-content h3 {
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            color: var(--text-main);
            font-size: 20px;
        }

        .timeline-content ul {
            padding-left: 20px;
            color: var(--text-muted);
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        .timeline-content li {
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body class="dashboard-body">

    <!-- Mobile Sidebar Overlay -->
    <div class="sidebar-overlay" id="sidebarOverlay"
        onclick="document.getElementById('sidebar').classList.remove('active')"></div>

    <nav class="sidebar" id="sidebar">
        <div class="sidebar-logo">
            <img src="/netigo-logo.png" alt="Netigo Logo" style="width: 40px; height: 40px; object-fit: contain;">
            <h2>Netigo Shareholder Dashboard</h2>
            <button class="hamburger-btn close-sidebar"
                onclick="document.getElementById('sidebar').classList.remove('active')">
                <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
                    <line x1="18" y1="6" x2="6" y2="18"></line>
                    <line x1="6" y1="6" x2="18" y2="18"></line>
                </svg>
            </button>
        </div>
        <div class="sidebar-menu">
            <a href="/" class="menu-item">
                <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
                    <path d="M3 9l9-7 9 7v11a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H5a2 2 0 0 1-2-2z"></path>
                    <polyline points="9 22 9 12 15 12 15 22"></polyline>
                </svg>
                Dashboard
            </a>

            <a href="/admin" class="menu-item">
                <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
                    <path d="M12 22s8-4 8-10V5l-8-3-8 3v7c0 6 8 10 8 10z"></path>
                </svg>
                Admin Panel
            </a>

            <% if (user.role==='superadmin' ) { %>
                <a href="/superadmin" class="menu-item">
                    <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
                        <path d="M12 22s8-4 8-10V5l-8-3-8 3v7c0 6 8 10 8 10z"></path>
                    </svg>
                    Superadmin
                </a>
                <% } %>

                    <a href="/updates" class="menu-item active" style="margin-top: auto;">
                        <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor"
                            stroke-width="2">
                            <circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"></circle>
                            <line x1="12" y1="16" x2="12" y2="12"></line>
                            <line x1="12" y1="8" x2="12.01" y2="8"></line>
                        </svg>
                        What's New
                    </a>

                    <a href="/logout" class="menu-item logout-btn">
                        <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor"
                            stroke-width="2">
                            <path d="M9 21H5a2 2 0 0 1-2-2V5a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h4"></path>
                            <polyline points="16 17 21 12 16 7"></polyline>
                            <line x1="21" y1="12" x2="9" y2="12"></line>
                        </svg>
                        Logout
                    </a>
        </div>
    </nav>

    <main class="main-content">
        <header class="topbar">
            <div class="topbar-header">
                <button class="hamburger-btn" onclick="document.getElementById('sidebar').classList.add('active')">
                    <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
                        <line x1="3" y1="12" x2="21" y2="12"></line>
                        <line x1="3" y1="6" x2="21" y2="6"></line>
                        <line x1="3" y1="18" x2="21" y2="18"></line>
                    </svg>
                </button>
                <div class="greeting">
                    <h1>Update History</h1>
                    <p>Netigo Shareholder Dashboard Changelog</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="topbar-actions">
                <a href="/" class="btn-secondary">
                    <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
                        <line x1="19" y1="12" x2="5" y2="12"></line>
                        <polyline points="12 19 5 12 12 5"></polyline>
                    </svg>
                    Back to Dashboard
                </a>
            </div>
        </header>

        <section class="content-grid" style="display: block; margin-top: 30px;">
            <div class="timeline">

                <div class="timeline-item">
                    <div class="timeline-content card">
                        <span class="version-badge">Version 1.2.0</span>
                        <span class="update-date">February 2026</span>
                        <h3>UI & UX Polishing</h3>
                        <ul>
                            <li><strong>Dropdown Overhaul:</strong> Replaced flat native &lt;select&gt; selectors across
                                the dashboard (Recurring Costs, Notes) with custom styled SVG chevrons for improved
                                interactivity.</li>
                            <li><strong>Button Standardization:</strong> Remapped the auxiliary navigation links on the
                                Updates page to inherit standardized `.btn-secondary` padding, hover boundaries, and
                                flexbox alignment.</li>
                            <li><strong>Notes Verification:</strong> Team Notes &amp; Tasks fully integrated into
                                GridStack.</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="timeline-item">
                    <div class="timeline-content card">
                        <span class="version-badge">Version 1.1.0</span>
                        <span class="update-date">February 2026</span>
                        <h3>Notes & Optimization Update</h3>
                        <ul>
                            <li><strong>Unified Updates Page:</strong> Moved the "What's New" modal into a dedicated,
                                paginated historical timeline view.</li>
                            <li><strong>Premium Branding:</strong> Polished Netigo typography credits and explicitly
                                rebranded application to Netigo Shareholder Dashboard.</li>
                            <li><strong>GridStack Defaults Improved:</strong> Patched the baseline Recurring Expenses
                                widget height to guarantee parallel top-row docking with Chart module out of the box.
                            </li>
                            <li><strong>Anti-Ghost Rendering Patch:</strong> Eliminated `localStorage` glitches where
                                widgets duplicated when re-rendering components using strict DOM ID binding.</li>
                            <li><strong>Universal Notes System (Coming Soon):</strong> Scaffolded groundwork for global
                                and personal Netigo team todo-lists across the dashboard views.</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="timeline-item">
                    <div class="timeline-content card" style="border-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.05);">
                        <span class="version-badge" style="background: var(--text-muted);">Version 1.0.0</span>
                        <span class="update-date">February 2026</span>
                        <h3>The Foundation</h3>
                        <ul>
                            <li><strong>Core Architecture:</strong> Initial release of the Next-Gen Shareholder view,
                                replacing legacy PHP overhead tracking.</li>
                            <li><strong>Role Based Access Control:</strong> Founders assigned Admin and Superadmin
                                security groups with secure bcrypt hashing.</li>
                            <li><strong>Drag & Drop Interface:</strong> Fully modular and responsive UI built primarily
                                on `GridStack.js`, allowing founders to independently rearrange their workflows directly
                                onto their browser's persistent cache.</li>
                            <li><strong>Automated 30-Day Audit Trails:</strong> Comprehensive logging payload
                                documenting all critical company operations automatically to keep the team aligned.</li>
                            <li><strong>Dynamic Categories & Projections:</strong> Configurable recurring timeline
                                filtering estimating forward-looking corporate expenses mathematically from daily to
                                yearly intervals.</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                </div>

            </div>
        </section>
    </main>

</body>

</html>